		{"cgact", file="cgact", id=2, lv=2, act="表示アクション", a1=0, a2=255, time=1000, a_chr=151, alpha=255},
		{"cgact", file="cgact", id=2, act="移動", x=-255, y=-5, time=10000, lv=2},
		{"text"},
		text = {
			ja = {
				{
					"*テキスト*",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			en = {
				{
					"It’s because I’ve found an interesting article on the protest we encountered near SHO headquarters earlier.",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			cn = {
				{
					"我注意到一篇，关于前段时间在SHO本部大楼前示威的文章。",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			tw = {
				{
					"我注意到一篇，關於前段時間在SHO本部大樓前示威的文章。",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
		},
		linkback = "0034_00283",
		linknext = "0034_00285",
		line = 3843,
	},
	["0034_00285"] = {
		{"text"},
		text = {
			ja = {
				{
					"*テキスト*",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			en = {
				{
					"Looks like that organization really is led by an “entrepreneur” who’s written all kinds of books on gender.",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			cn = {
				{
					"该示威组织的高层，似乎是个出版各种性别理论主题的书籍、这样的一个“生意人”。",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			tw = {
				{
					"該示威組織的高層，似乎是個出版各種性別理論主題的書籍、這樣的一個「生意人」。",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
		},
		linkback = "0034_00284",
		linknext = "0034_00286",
		line = 3853,
	},
	["0034_00286"] = {
		{"text"},
		text = {
			ja = {
				{
					"*テキスト*",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			en = {
				{
					"And it seems like she got into this line of work after an online controversy.",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			cn = {
				{
					"看来似乎是因为网络上的争议，她才开始做“这份工作”的。",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			tw = {
				{
					"看來似乎是因為網路上的爭議，她才開始做「這份工作」的。",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
		},
		linkback = "0034_00285",
		linknext = "0034_00287",
		line = 3863,
	},
	["0034_00287"] = {
		{"text"},
		text = {
			ja = {
				{
					"*テキスト*",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			en = {
				{
					"It started when one account—I can’t figure out whose, since the details are blurred—used social media to make an appeal.",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			cn = {
				{
					"这场争论最开始似乎某个帐户──因为被上了马赛克所以我看不出是什么──透过社群网络提出的抱怨。",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			tw = {
				{
					"這場爭論最開始似乎某個帳戶──因為被上了馬賽克所以我看不出是什麼──透過社群網路提出的抱怨。",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
		},
		linkback = "0034_00286",
		linknext = "0034_00288",
		line = 3873,
	},
	["0034_00288"] = {
		{"text"},
		text = {
			ja = {
				{
					"*テキスト*",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			en = {
				{
					"They were raising questions about how sex is recognized on Seiran Island.",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			cn = {
				{
					"它提出了有关青蓝岛上的性别意识问题。",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			tw = {
				{
					"它提出了有關青藍島上的性別意識問題。",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
		},
		linkback = "0034_00287",
		linknext = "0034_00289",
		line = 3883,
	},
	["0034_00289"] = {
		{"text"},
		text = {
			ja = {
				{
					"*テキスト*",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			en = {
				{
					"It seems like while their tone was extreme, their arguments did make sense.",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			cn = {
				{
					"虽然文章的内容是激进的，但论证的基调是连贯的。",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			tw = {
				{
					"雖然文章的內容是激進的，但論證的基調是連貫的。",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
		},
		linkback = "0034_00288",
		linknext = "0034_00290",
		line = 3893,
	},
	["0034_00290"] = {
		{"text"},
		text = {
			ja = {
				{
					"*テキスト*",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			en = {
				{
					"They said that while the island called itself a place of freedom, it existed upon the premise that all people could be divided into either male or female.",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			cn = {
				{
					"青蓝岛虽然被命名为自由岛，但它是一个以区分“性别”作为前提的地方。",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			tw = {
				{
					"青藍島雖然被命名為自由島，但它是一個以區分「性別」作為前提的地方。",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
		},
		linkback = "0034_00289",
		linknext = "0034_00291",
		line = 3903,
	},
	["0034_00291"] = {
		{"text"},
		text = {
			ja = {
				{
					"*テキスト*",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			en = {
				{
					"The island regulated clothing, rejected homosexuality, and believed that men are men, and women are women.",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			cn = {
				{
					"对服装的限制，对同性恋的排斥，男人就是男人，女人就是女人的认知意识──",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			tw = {
				{
					"對服裝的限制，對同性戀的排斥，男人就是男人，女人就是女人的認知意識──",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
		},
		linkback = "0034_00290",
		linknext = "0034_00292",
		line = 3913,
	},
	["0034_00292"] = {
		{"text"},
		text = {
			ja = {
				{
					"*テキスト*",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			en = {
				{
					"As a result, its application of a strict gender binary as though it’s a natural part of perverted sex is a form of unconscious discrimination.",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			cn = {
				{
					"这是一种将性别歧视带入了变态做爱之中、无意识产生的歧视。",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			tw = {
				{
					"這是一種將性別歧視帶入了變態做愛之中、無意識產生的歧視。",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
		},
		linkback = "0034_00291",
		linknext = "0034_00293",
		line = 3923,
	},
	["0034_00293"] = {
		{"text"},
		text = {
			ja = {
				{
					"*テキスト*",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			en = {
				{
					"This individual continued to rail against the island, hashtagging each post.",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			cn = {
				{
					"该人添加了一个Tag并继续抱怨。",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			tw = {
				{
					"該人添加了一個Tag並繼續抱怨。",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
		},
		linkback = "0034_00292",
		linknext = "0034_00294",
		line = 3933,
	},
	["0034_00294"] = {
		{"se", id=0, loop=0, file="se_a121"},
		{"cgdel", id=2, lv=2, time=500, alphadel=1},
		{"fg", file="jun_01f_00003", file1="jun_01f_00101", file2="jun_01f_00204", path=":fg/jun_01f/", id=30, ch="淳之介", lv=2, mw="mw", mode=1, sync=0, x=-5, y=-5},
		{"text"},
		text = {
			ja = {
				{
					name = {"淳之介"},
					"*テキスト*",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			en = {
				{
					name = {"淳之介", "Junnosuke"},
					"“...”",
					{"rt2"},
